g.title: AWS CloudFormation Sample Template Rails_Single_Instance: Create a Ruby on Rails stack using a single EC2 instance with a local MySQL database for storage. This template demonstrates using the AWS CloudFormation bootstrap scripts to install the packages and files necessary to deploy the packages and files at instance launch time. **WARNING** This template creates an Amazon EC2 instance. You will be billed for the AWS resources used if you create a stack from this template.
